@startuml clubos-seq-pagamento
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Tesoureiro" as T
participant "Web" as W
participant "Payments API" as API
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "BullMQ" as Q
participant "Worker PDF" as WK
participant "MinIO/S3" as S3

T -> W: Regista pagamento
W -> API: POST /api/payments
API -> DB: INSERT Payment
API -> DB: Actualizar quota
API -> Q: enqueue recibo
API -> DB: AuditLog
API --> W: 201
Q -> WK: process job
WK -> S3: upload PDF
WK -> DB: estado emissão = ready

@enduml
